    Completed 2026-06-11. All 5 validation checks PASS. (1) MCP describe returned all 10 sprk_* fields with correct types/sizes/nullability. (2) Web API confirmed seed row c46b940e-4b65-f111-ab0c-70a8a590c51c with all 9 business fields exactly matching Task 013 notes; Q-U1 and Q-U2 compliance reaffirmed. (3) Alt-key query by sprk_topicname='matter-health' returned exactly 1 row (FR-05 mount-check filter shape confirmed). (4) Both forms present with formids matching Task 012 exactly: Main 1823746f-4665-f111-ab0c-7ced8ddc4cc6, Quick Create 5523746f-4665-f111-ab0c-7ced8ddc4cc6. (5) Report authored at notes/handoffs/phase-1-validation.md with explicit "Phase 2 cleared to start" statement (legacy framing — actual practical effect is Phase 7 production-deploy readiness gate since Phase 2 already complete except Task 025 parallel sibling). No blockers. No drift between handoff records and live Dataverse state.
